      "text": "Creatinine-only CKD-EPI 2021 (race-free) with optional 2009 equation."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Inputs: sex, age, creatinine (mg/dL or umol/L), race (2009 only)."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Results"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "eGFR normalized to 1.73 m^2 body surface area."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "GFR categories (KDIGO)"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "items": [
        "G1: >= 90 (Normal or high)",
        "G2: 60-89 (Mildly decreased)",
        "G3a: 45-59 (Mildly to moderately decreased)",
        "G3b: 30-44 (Moderately to severely decreased)",
        "G4: 15-29 (Severely decreased)",
        "G5: < 15 (Kidney failure)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Disclaimer"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Reference only; use pediatric equations for patients under 18 years and interpret results in clinical context."
